strings: <voice_0x01000B77><se_def>China: Are you... the only one I see in the bar? What are you doing here?
<voice_0x01000B78><se_high>Accuracy: What do you mean what are you doing here? You'll find out! Now that we've got that stupid ring back, let's go!
<voice_0x01000B79><se_def>China: katamas..?
<voice_0x01000B7A><se_def>China: congested! This card is still playable!
<voice_0x01000B7B><se_def>China: View! I have a request
<voice_0x01000B7C><se_high>Accuracy: are you kidding me please
<voice_0x01000B7D><se_high>Accuracy: why i want to help you
<voice_0x01000B7E><se_def>China: Listen, it's all right! It's time to speak!
<voice_0x01000B7F><se_def>China: ...You don't know? Don't you think there's a creepy feeling in the temple?
<voice_0x01000B80><se_def>China: I heard that the Joker is on his way to the principal's office. Where do you think bad breath comes from?
<voice_0x01000B81><se_high>Accuracy: A proposal!
<voice_0x01000B82><se_def>China: I don't know what he will do. But of course Dean Francisco's life is in danger!
<voice_0x01000B83><se_def>China: Need help? I want to go to my uncle's house. And see if everything is fine.
<voice_0x01000B84><se_def>China: I did not ask, can I go alone? But today this is impossible.
<voice_0x01000B85><se_def>China: We promise to repay you! Are the priests safe?
<voice_0x01000B86><se_def>China: ...Thank you. listen to me now
<voice_0x01000B87><se_def>China: You must have seen this too. But stubborn fools guard the bridge to Abbott Hall, I can't go on.
<voice_0x01000B88><se_def>China: However, if you want to go shopping, there are other ways to get it.
<voice_0x01000B89><se_def>China: You have to leave the monastery like a commoner. But you need to turn right, then left along the river.
<voice_0x01000B8A><se_def>China: only to clean the river and keep the monastery alive
<voice_0x01000B8B><se_def>China: Follow the river to the ruins. It is a former royal monastery that has been in use since ancient times.
<voice_0x01000B8C><se_def>China: Then there's an underground passage leading to the father-in-law's house.
<voice_0x01000B8D><se_def>China: Unfortunately this is the only way.
<voice_0x01000B8E><se_def>China: You can use the shrine ring you gave him to open the entrance to the ruins. So, go, okay?
<voice_0x01000B8F><se_def>China: But had no time to think! Now you must rescue the priest!
